[Contract "6H"]
[Result ""]
[Auction "S"]
2C pass 2D pass 2H pass 3H pass 4NT pass 5C pass 5D pass 6H pass pass pass
[BCFlags "1f"]
[RotationNote "Board 3, chOption: S, chBasis: S, basisKind:Declarer, nOption:2, nBasis: 2, nRot: 0, useStandardVul: true"]
[Category "Partnership Bidding"]
[Difficulty "advanced"]
[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/roman_key_card"]
[Student "S"]
{This is the companion to Deal 22.

Again, worried about a possible trump loser in addition to the missing Ace, SOUTH 
bids 5\D, the Queen Ask.

NORTH definitely does NOT have the \HQ. But with five trumps she 
does know that SOUTH probably does not have a trump loser so she jumps 
to 6\H anyway.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
