[Category "Partnership Bidding"]
[Difficulty "advanced"]
[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/roman_key_card"]
[Student "S"]
{EAST cannot use RKCB at her second bid because trumps have not been agreed. So she bids 
3\H to set trumps, knowing WEST cannot pass after her jump-shift. 

WEST tries to stop at game but EAST is too strong so she now uses RKCB and gets 
to 6\H when WEST shows two Key Cards and the trump Queen.}

